       "text": "Trains run nonstop from Manhattan to Jamaica. Port Washington Branch trains continue to stop at Woodside in both directions.\n\nThe subway will allow LIRR riders to enter the following stations at no cost:\n34 St-Penn Station [E]\n42 St-Grand Central [6][7]\nWoodside-61 St [7]\nForest Hills-71 Av [E]\nKew Gardens-Union Turnpike [E]\nPresent your LIRR ticket to the station booth agent for access to the subway system.\n\nWhat's happening?\nAccessibility improvements and track maintenance",
       "language": "en"
      },
      {
