      {
       "text": "<p>Eastbound trains skip <strong>Hollis</strong>, <strong>Queens Village</strong>, and <strong>Elmont-UBS Arena</strong></p>",
       "language": "en-html"
      }
     ]
    },
    "description_text": {
     "translation": [
      {
       "text": "MTA buses will accept LIRR tickets for travel from Jamaica to Hollis and Queens Village. View a map of your route options.\nNICE buses will accept LIRR tickets for travel from Jamaica to Elmont-UBS Arena.\n\nFollow this link for information about transferring at the Jamaica Bus Terminal.\n\nConcert attendees traveling to and from UBS Arena may also take a westbound train via transfer at Jamaica or Mineola at no additional charge. This option will not appear in the TrainTime app.\n\nThis service change will occur on most weekends through late August as we replace and install switches near Elmont-UBS Arena.",
       "language": "en"
      },
      {
       "text": "<p>MTA buses will accept LIRR tickets for travel from <strong>Jamaica</strong> to <strong>Hollis</strong> and <strong>Queens Village</strong>. <a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.mta.info/image/186256\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" data-link-auto=\"\" target=\"_blank\">View a map of your route options</a><a title=\"\" href=\"https://new.mta.info/sites/default/files/2024-07/LIRR%20PSC.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" data-link-auto=\"\" target=\"_blank\">.</a></p><p>NICE buses will accept LIRR tickets for travel from <strong>Jamaica</strong> to <strong>Elmont-UBS Arena</strong>.</p><p style=\"min-height:10px\"></p><p>Follow <a title=\"\" href=\"https://new.mta.info/stations/jamaica/local-buses\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" data-link-auto=\"\" target=\"_blank\">this link</a> for information about transferring at the Jamaica Bus Terminal.</p><p style=\"min-height:10px\"></p><p>Concert attendees traveling to and from UBS Arena may also take a westbound train via transfer at <strong>Jamaica</strong> or <strong>Mineola</strong> at no additional charge. This option will not appear in the TrainTime app.</p><p style=\"min-height:10px\"></p><p><a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.mta.info/article/summer-lirr-service-changes-2026\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" data-link-auto=\"\" target=\"_blank\">This service change will occur on most weekends through late August</a> as we replace and install switches near <strong>Elmont-UBS Arena</strong>.</p>",
       "language": "en-html"
      }
     ]
    },
